parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The battery drain and failure can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leaving the driver stranded and potentially unsafe.
symptoms: The battery dies frequently
the vehicle won't start
the battery drains quickly
the vehicle's electrical system malfunctions
and the vehicle's lights and accessories may not function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system malfunctions can cause the vehicle's systems to fail, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The vehicle's electrical system malfunctions
the battery drains quickly
the vehicle's lights and accessories may not function properly
and the vehicle's systems may not operate as intended.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power and mobility, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The transmission fails
the vehicle loses power and mobility
and the vehicle may not shift gears properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexplained cracking of the windshield can obstruct the driver's view, causing a safety hazard and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Windshield cracks or shatters without any apparent reason
often with no visible impact or chip; cracks may spread rapidly
sometimes within hours or days; cracks may occur in various locations on the windshield
including the top
middle
or bottom.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips
shudders
or hesitates when accelerating
especially at high speeds; the vehicle loses power or stalls; the transmission makes abnormal noises
such as grinding or whining sounds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause accidents or injuries, especially if the vehicle is unable to stop in time.
symptoms: The brakes shudder or vibrate when applied; the brakes make loud noises; the brakes fail to engage properly
leading to extended stopping distances.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery can leave the driver stranded, especially if the vehicle is unable to start in an emergency situation.
symptoms: The battery drains frequently
even when the vehicle is turned off; no warning lights or indicators appear to alert the driver to the battery drain.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and hesitation can cause loss of control, accidents, and leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips
resulting in a lengthy wait time until it revs to the next gear
and then there is a palpable "jolt" as the transmission appears to move into the next gear
hesitation before the car actually accelerates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The windshield cracking can cause distracted driving, panic, and accidents due to the sudden and loud cracking noise.
symptoms: The windshield cracks suddenly and loudly
often without any apparent reason
and can spread rapidly across the windshield.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The gasoline smell and fumes can cause health problems, nausea, and dizziness, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Strong smell of gasoline in the vehicle
often when the fan is on
and fumes coming out of the vents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The battery life issues can cause the vehicle to not start, leading to inconvenience, and potentially causing accidents if the vehicle is stranded on the road.
symptoms: The battery drains prematurely
often without any warning
and may require jump-starting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system issues can cause the vehicle to shut off while driving, leading to accidents, and potentially cause electrical fires.
symptoms: The engine shuts off while driving
and the Multi-Function Display and STARLINK Multimedia touchscreen may malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The clutch and transmission-related issues can cause loss of control, accidents, and leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
and the transmission may slip or hesitate.
